 And I guess "dlm not being marked experimental for a long time" meant
 three months.

 net/sctp/Kconfig | 4 ++--
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

diff --git a/net/sctp/Kconfig b/net/sctp/Kconfig
